1. *Tvrdi* da će nastaviti da radi (He claims he will continue to work).
2. Ona *tvrdi* da je završila zadatak (She insists she has finished the task).
3. On *tvrdi* da je njegov najbolji prijatelj (He claims that his best friend).
4. Ne *tvrdi* da si u pravu (Don't insist that you are right).
5. Oni *tvrde* da će biti tu (They claim they will be there).